<plot>H.A.U.L. is the police department's elite Hoisting and Urgent Lifting Unit. After receiving a frantic call from Rick Panda to save his father who lies helpless under a refrigerator, the H.A.U.L. team springs into action! Using G.R.A.V.I., a multimillion dollar computer program located in the back of the H.A.U.L. van, RATCHET and his pet robot ENGLAND DAN create an elaborate schematic of ropes and pulleys to lift the fridge. With SPOTTER keeping lookout from the rooftop next door and MANGLER waiting outside for pull-pull time", CAPTAIN O'HAIRE and MUSTANG race against time to save poor Mr. Panda. Get your head in the game and Make the call. The call for H.A.U.L.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?226215</url></doc>
